 \frac{7x^2+2x-7}{x^3-x} = \frac{7x^2+2x-7}{x(x^2-1)} = \frac{7x^2+2x-7}{x(x-1)(x+1)} 
 \frac{7x^2+2x-7}{x(x-1)(x+1)} = \frac{A}{x} + \frac{B}{(x-1)} + \frac{C}{(x+1)} 
